name: VGG_S Image Labeler

pipes.description: Please upload a png or jpg image.
pipes.name: One by one prediction

description:
This predictor is based on the example for the python library Lasagne available at https://github.com/Lasagne/Recipes/blob/master/examples/ImageNet%20Pretrained%20Network%20(VGG_S).ipynb

You can find the source code of this onine demo at: https://github.com/predictors/VGG_S_Image_Labeler

It demonstrates using a network pretrained on ImageNet for classification. The model used was converted from the VGG_CNN_S model (http://arxiv.org/abs/1405.3531) in Caffe's Model Zoo.

For details of the conversion process, see the example notebook "Usinga Caffe Pretrained Network - CIFAR10"
